00:07:27.750 --> 00:07:31.190
I ended up with about 80,000
individual slave values,

00:07:31.190 --> 00:07:34.270
as I mentioned, appraisal
and market sales.

00:07:34.270 --> 00:07:38.020
Some of this came from insurance
records were people were ensuring

00:07:38.020 --> 00:07:42.880
their enslaved people from as young
as age nine to as old as age 89

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:46.790
or 90, life insurance policies so
that if the enslaved person passed,

00:07:46.790 --> 00:07:49.120
