00:08:10.820 --> 00:08:12.580
And this is what I came up with.

00:08:12.580 --> 00:08:14.030
This is what I found.

00:08:14.030 --> 00:08:17.640
This is a slide -- I realize when
I've been talking about my book,

00:08:17.640 --> 00:08:19.730
I've been sharing the
stories of the enslaved,

00:08:19.730 --> 00:08:22.580
which is the most important part
