00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:10.900
the number of enslaved people
folks owned, that's a lot of money.

00:09:10.900 --> 00:09:16.590
And a lot of these people had
large plantations, 300 people.

00:09:16.590 --> 00:09:19.750
They sometimes had more
money in human bodies

00:09:19.750 --> 00:09:22.070
and human chattel than
