00:09:22.070 --> 00:09:24.290 position:56%
So that's something to keep in mind.

00:09:24.290 --> 00:09:28.120
I can come back to this slide
later during the Q&amp;A if you like.

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:32.540 position:56%
This is just an example of a bill of
sale, just one sample of the types

00:09:32.540 --> 00:09:35.990
of records that I used
to characterize

00:09:35.990 --> 00:09:37.820
and find this information.

00:09:37.820 --> 00:09:39.590
But one of the things
