00:37:32.630 --> 00:37:36.940
and maybe the kind of
anthropological element of it

00:37:36.940 --> 00:37:43.030
in terms of I know that up until
probably only the last five decades

00:37:43.030 --> 00:37:46.780
or so there was a lot of kind of
hair-splitting between the idea

00:37:46.780 --> 00:37:49.220
of people of different races
being different species.

00:37:49.220 --> 00:37:53.110
So as these cadavers are being
brought in and being tested

00:37:53.110 --> 00:37:56.470
and being examined, are
they kind of feeding some

00:37:56.470 --> 00:38:01.510 position:56%
of those very racist ideas,
species-ist ideas or are they looked

00:38:01.510 --> 00:38:04.720
at as, "Well, hey, we have body
that we can finally look at.

00:38:04.720 --> 00:38:06.020
Let's make the" --

00:38:06.020 --> 00:38:07.320
