00:50:20.850 --> 00:50:22.150
to decide how deep I wanted to go.

00:50:22.150 --> 00:50:23.450
I have some of the values of
his enslaved people in the book,

00:50:23.450 --> 00:50:24.750
but they're part of the dataset.

00:50:24.750 --> 00:50:26.050
But what I did with Jefferson
here, just at the beginning

00:50:26.050 --> 00:50:27.350
of the introduction I have a quote
